<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="charity-n">charity <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tʃærəti/    美 /'tʃærəti/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] 慈善（事业）；[C] 慈善机构 / 团体：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>raise money for charity</strong>
为慈善事业筹款</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a charity concert / dinner</strong>
慈善音乐会/宴会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some companies find it not enough to simply donate money to charities.
有些公司发现仅仅向慈善机构捐钱是不够的。</p><footer>2014 上海改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2u">2.<strong>[U]［正式用语］慈悲；宽容：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Newspaper reports <strong>showed</strong> him little <strong>charity</strong>.
报纸的报道对他毫不宽容。</p></div></div>